comments: Mathurin (IND) is moving toward and makes contact with Jackson's (MEM) body while he is airborne, which affects his ability to secure the pass.
Williams Jr. (MEM) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with Nesmith's (IND) arm after the release.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) briefly grasps Siakam's (IND) arm and marginal contact occurs before Jackson Jr. picks up his dribble.
Mathurin (IND) legally contests Jackson's (MEM) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) immediately slides his hand off of Siakam's (IND) side and marginal contact occurs as Siakam moves toward the perimeter.
Siakam (IND) brings his hands toward Konchar (MEM) and marginal contact occurs as they briefly engage and immediately disengage.
Siakam (IND) slides his resting hand off Konchar's (MEM) body and marginal contact occurs as Siakam releases at the end of the drive.
Konchar (MEM) legally contests Siakam's (IND) jump shot attempt.
Smith (IND) initiates contact with Jackson's (MEM) head during the pass attempt.
Konchar (MEM) brings his arm toward the ball and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Nembhard's (IND) arm at the end of the drive.
Williams Jr. (MEM) brings his arm toward the ball on his contest and some contact occurs with Smith's (IND) arm as he completes the dunk.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) fumbles the ball upon receiving the pass and legally regains control before starting his dribble.
Siakam (IND) legally contests Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) shot attempt in the lane.
Roddy (MEM) and Mathurin (IND) briefly come together as Mathurin secures the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.

Jackson Jr. (MEM) brings his arm toward the ball and Nembhard (IND) briefly grasps Jackson Jr.'s extended arm before they quickly disengage. Jackson Jr. then makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it from Nembhard.
Nesmith (IND) dives to the floor to recover the loose ball and is granted the timeout that he requests prior to Konchar's (MEM) attempt to tie it up for a jump ball.
Roddy (MEM) commits a take foul on Nembhard (IND). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Williams Jr. (MEM) commits a take foul on Nembhard (IND). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) extends toward the basket and into Siakam's (IND) vertical arm as incidental contact occurs during the shot attempt.
Roddy's (MEM) arms extend out slightly when he disengages from Smith (IND) and marginal contact occurs as Smith secures the rebound.
